org.oddjob.arooa

Interface ArooaParser

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DesignParser, StandardArooaParser, StandardFragmentParser, XMLArooaParser

    public interface ArooaParser
    An ArooaConfigurationParser is able to parse an ArooaConfiguration.

    The parser will either produce a ArooaText object or throw an ArooaParseException if parsing fails.
